data.title: Liesel Pritzker Simmons
data.text:
See also Wikipedia's article about "Liesel Pritzker Simmons".

Liesel Pritzker Simmons CC(?) 2006(?) is an actress who has starred in several movies, including A Little Princess (1995) and Air Force One. She from the Pritzker family, which owns the Hyatt Hotel in Chicago. She uses the stage name "Liesel Matthews" to honor her brother, Matthew, and to avoid conflict with her divorced parents.
